      <link>https://alexandervossen.github.io/post/2022-03-28-welcome/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://alexandervossen.github.io/post/2022-03-28-welcome/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;new-page-launched&#34;&gt;New page launched!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am very happy that I have finally found the time to compile this new site that focuses on my work as a researcher. On it, you can find announcements for talks, teaching materials, papers, data, code and everything else that has to do with my work. Also, I will share some (hopefully) nifty tricks that I learned in my ten years as an empirical researcher that utilizes large-scale secondary data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy reading and browsing and feel free to drop me a mail in case you have any questions!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
